abstract.value: The Time Inc. News Clippings contain copies of news articles about Time Warner and AOL Time Warner, its publications, and its subsidiaries.

p.value: Open to qualified researchers. Materials are stored offsite and advance notice is required for use.
This record group should be cited as Time Inc. News Clippings, MS 3009-RG 20, New-York Historical Society.

The Time Inc. News Clippings contain copies of news articles about Time Warner and AOL Time Warner, its publications, and its subsidiaries collected by the Time Inc. Library and Archives. Corporate Communications compiled some of the clippings packets. Gaps in dates indicate clippings were not located, and it is unknown if folders of these clippings exist.

subject.value: Publishers and publishing -- New York (State)  -- New York.
